plot: 054 : The Eldest Namek, Guru, unlocks Krillin's hidden potential. Zarbon reports to Frieza and is told to retrieve Vegeta's battered body for interrogation. Gohan goes after the Dragon Ball that had been hidden by Vegeta.

Guru unlocks Krillin's hidden potential. Zarbon reports to Frieza only to be sent out to retrieve Vegeta's battered body for interrogation. Gohan goes after the Dragon Ball that Vegeta hid; Goku can't move after his latest training session.—Zabon
